description:
Morning Cuties! Christmas might be over but Chanukah has just begun! 
Join us at Cougar for the last Thirsty Thursday before the new year. If you haven't been to a Firsts this year, this is your last chance ;)

Don't forget a headlamp and navigation!

8m & 2,200ft: https://www.strava.com/routes/3307073711249075950
6m & 1770ft: https://www.strava.com/routes/3307073474274644214
3m & 1200ft: https://www.strava.com/routes/3307074303650607350
title: 12/26 | Thirsty Firsts | Cougar

description:
Come on out to the iconic Q20 where drinks are cheap and you can bring in any food - including from the convenient aisles of QFC! Enjoy one of the three routes and the company of good people!

Routes:
3Mi | 200' | Pace Groups 10+/- min/mi
https://www.strava.com/routes/3306827063293732714

5.5 Mi | 400' | Pace Groups 8:30, 10+/-

9mi | 800' | Pace Groups 7:45, 8:30 10+/-
https://www.strava.com/routes/3306720512711871734

Post-Social at Q20 (QFC bar)

Headlamp! 

Note: you may want to bring  your own navigation in case there are not enough leaders due to the holidays
title: Thirsty Seconds | Q20
